beri dia pelajaran.

101
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,240
Liu Qianshui?

102
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:02,680
Di dunia yang dulu, dia datang
dari Benua Xuanling.

103
00:08:02,990 --> 00:08:05,960
Dia menemukanku saat sedang
mencari pemilik Mutiara Zhenhun.

104
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,960
Lalu, dia juga memberiku
seruling pengusir roh.

105
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:11,120
Benua Xuanling?

106
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:13,310
Apa? Mutiara apa?

107
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,310
Seruling pengusir roh?

108
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:19,080
Kawan, apa kau masih punya
banyak pertanyaan lagi?

109
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:23,200
Aku lupa kalian sudah tak ingat.

110
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,470
Jing Xin.

111
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,270
Mana si Pengkhianat?

112
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,590
Sudah aku ikat.

113
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:32,870
Kau berani menipuku.

114
