123
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,240
Jelas-jelas namamu Liu Baishui.

124
00:08:57,300 --> 00:08:59,960
Kenapa kau menipuku dan bilang
namamu 'Liu Qianshui'?<i>*Qian, ribuan</i>

125
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,450
Aku tak menipu Tuan Putri.

126
00:09:01,450 --> 00:09:03,580
Sejak awal, kubilang
namaku 'Liu Baishui'.<i>*Bai, ratusan</i>

127
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,790
